            <!-- Stemmatics -->
            <note type="stemmatics">A work called K. al-nafs wa-huwa k. al-Zumurruda al-khaḍrāʾ
                  is mentioned in ʿUqlat al-mustawfiz. It is also part of RG 434. OY lists only two
                  mss. for this work. Berlin 3001 is very late, and there is nothing on the work to
                  indicate that it is by IA. We have not managed to inspect the other, Ismail Saïb
                  1197. ‘Abd al-Baqi Miftah has edited this, and Claude Addas believes it to be
                  authentic.</note>
